    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable transportation or a practical project opportunity. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values straightforward value over cosmetics, but it still presents as a worthwhile option for commuting, light use, or improvement over time. A sensible choice for someone seeking low upfront cost and plenty of potential.",
