      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride with plenty of life left to give? This car is a solid budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transportation, a project, or a dependable backup vehicle. It\u2019s not perfect, but it\u2019s honest, priced right, and could be a great fit for the right buyer who doesn\u2019t mind a little TLC. If you want simple value without spending a fortune, this one is worth a look.",
